      "review_summary": "The PR adds provider code-only failover classifications in the core error classifier and expands agent classifier tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +29, Tests +77. Total +106 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible. Current main and v2026.6.10 only classify generic codes and return empty_response for message-less code-only signals, while the PR's tests and Real behavior proof cover the missing path.",
